SSH 填写示例

示例 1：平时这样连接
ssh user@xxx.company.com

填写：
Host: xxx.company.com
User: user
Port: 22

示例 2：平时指定端口
ssh -p 2222 user@1.2.3.4

填写：
Host: 1.2.3.4
User: user
Port: 2222

示例 3：平时用 SSH config alias
ssh company-dev

填写：
Host: company-dev
User: 留空
Port: 22

常用查询命令：
whoami
ls ~/.claude/projects
ls ~/.codex/sessions
find ~/.claude/projects -name "*.jsonl" | head
find ~/.codex/sessions -name "*.jsonl" | head

默认路径：
Claude Code: ~/.claude/projects
Codex: ~/.codex/sessions
